Disclaimer:
This website is not a fundraising service and will never attempt to collect money or payment information from you. You should only enter payment information on the https://hope.huntsmancancer.org/ domain, and never on this website.
 
 This website displays data collected directly from [Huntsman Challenge](https://hope.huntsmancancer.org/huntsmanchallenge/). This website shows totals raised by teams, including funds donated to the Huntsman Challenge outside of the Huntsman Challenge website, such as sending a check to Sigma Chi.
 
 The Sigma Chi International Fraternity in no way endorses any information displayed on this website. For their officially endorsed Huntsman Challenge, please visit [Huntsman Challenge](https://hope.huntsmancancer.org/huntsmanchallenge/).
 
 This Website uses HTML Local Storage (*not cookies*) to save your team selection. This website tracks usage statistics using Google Analytics.

SaveToPhone:
This website can be saved to your phone and appear as an App. Just follow a few simple steps below, depending on your phone type.
 
![Derby Dashboard saved on an iPhone Home Screen](/icon_on_home.png)
 
 ### iPhone w/ Safari
1. Navigate to the [homepage](/)
2. Tap the Share button
3. Scroll the grey action buttons to the left
4. Tap **Add to Home Screen**
5. Tap **Add** in the top-right corner
 
### Android w/ Chrome
1. Navigate to the [homepage](/)
2. Tap the More button in the top-right
3. Tap **Add to Home screen**
 
*For alternative Android web browsers, follow [this guide](https://www.wikihow.com/Set-a-Bookmark-Shortcut-in-Your-Home-Screen-on-Android) from wiki-how.*
SignUpForTexts:
This website offers optional text message alerts. The extent of the alerts will be to inform you of the events taking place during each Derby Day. If you sign up, you will receive one message each day that events occur, and nothing more.
 
An example message might look like
 
> DERBY> Todays events:
> SignASig @All Day
> Volleyball @7pm
> Details: http://bit.ly/12345
